title: BRIEF-Finjan Files Patent Infringement Complaint Against Carbon Black Inc

organizations.name: brief-finjan files patent infringement complaint against carbon black inc

text: March 22, 2018 / 5:43 PM / Updated 5 minutes ago BRIEF-Finjan Files Patent Infringement Complaint Against Carbon Black Inc Reuters Staff March 22 (Reuters) - Finjan Holdings Inc: * FINJAN FILES A PATENT INFRINGEMENT COMPLAINT AGAINST CARBON BLACK, INC. * FINJAN HOLDINGS INC SAYS ‍ITS SUBSIDIARY FINJAN, INC HAS FILED A PATENT INFRINGEMENT LAWSUIT AGAINST CARBON BLACK​ * FINJAN HOLDINGS-FINJAN FILED COMPLAINT, ON MARCH 21, AND ALLEGES THAT CARBON BLACK’S PRODUCTS AND SERVICES INFRINGE AT LEAST FOUR U.S. FINJAN PATENTS​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
